Title: Series: Raccolta di 60 stampe dei più celebri pitture di Verona
Description: Plate 24: A bishop in the sky flanked by putti, below at left another bishop and at right St Antony; after a painting by Battista Angolo del Moro from the church of San Fermo in Verona Etching
Curator's comments: From a series of plates engraved by Zancon and reproducing paintings then in Verona.
Associated names: Representation of: St Antony of Egypt
